<font color="#FF0000">REPLY TO TOM</font><br>
<tt>Wed Jun  4 21:20:06 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Tom,<br><br>
Thanks for reminding me about the destruction of Vietnam. It is a beautiful country with a gracious people whom I would rather have visited under better circumstances. This is one of those little agonies that I try to balance out with the rest of it....really just one conflict after another.<br><br>
I have compassion for the children, especially the children, who by no fault of their own were irrevocably scarred for life in ways that I can deeply appreciate. The eyes haunt me, and there were circumstances that stand out still in my mind as sticks deep in the sand, never to be carried off in the tide.<br><br>
For them, I would do anything. I mean....anything.<br><br>
Art
